frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts tiny chefs working diligently on a giant hamburger. The chefs are positioned on ladders, adding sesame seeds and cheese to the towering burger. The burger is stacked with lettuce, tomatoes, cheese, and two beef patties, all on a wooden board.
frames.description: The scene is set in a playful, imaginative kitchen environment where miniature chefs are preparing an oversized hamburger. The focus is on the interaction between the tiny figures and the large food item, creating a humorous and surreal atmosphere.
